OL,3,CAston Villa thrash Freiburg in
OL,4,CIstanbul to win first European trophy
OL,5,Cin 44 years
OL,7,FAston Villa have beaten Freiburg in
OL,8,FIstanbul to win their first European
OL,9,Ftrophy in 44 years.
OL,11,FUnai Emery's side took the field to
OL,12,Fface the German side in Besiktas Park
OL,13,Fon Wednesday evening.
OL,15,FThe players from both sides were
OL,16,Fwelcomed by flags of claret and blue
OL,17,Fat one end, while at the other was a
OL,18,Fsea of red.
