OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779383153
OL,3,CAston Villa thrash Freiburg in
OL,4,CIstanbul to win first European trophy
OL,5,Cin 44 years
OL,7,FIt was a tight afair from the get-go,
OL,8,Fwith both sides having a chance.
OL,9,FAlmost like boxers, they seized each
OL,10,Fother up.
OL,12,FBut it was the side from Birmingham
OL,13,Fthat dealt the first blow.
OL,15,FThe Belgian Youri Tielemans was free
OL,16,Fin the box as the ball was floated
OL,17,Finto him. He pulled his leg back and
OL,18,Ffired the ball into the net.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779383153
OL,3,CAston Villa thrash Freiburg in
OL,4,CIstanbul to win first European trophy
OL,5,Cin 44 years
OL,7,FVilla takes the lead. However, they
OL,8,Fdidn't stop there. As the pressure
OL,9,Ffrom Aston Villa grew.
OL,11,FEuropean finals can be the stage for
OL,12,Fspecial moments, and that is exactly
OL,13,Fwhat happened when Emi Buendia stepped
OL,14,Finto the spotlight.
OL,16,FIt felt like time had stopped when his
OL,17,Feffort from outside the box curled
OL,18,Finto the net to make it two for Villa.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
