PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779383153
OL,3,CAston Villa thrash Freiburg in
OL,4,CIstanbul to win first European trophy
OL,5,Cin 44 years
OL,7,FBack in Birmingham, fans who couldn't
OL,8,Fbe in Istanbul were watching the game
OL,9,Fat the Utilita Arena and just like in
OL,10,FTurkiye, were going crazy for their
OL,11,Fclub.
OL,13,FThe Villains went bouncing into half-
OL,14,Ftime. 15 important minutes for Unai
OL,15,FEmery, more of the same in the second
OL,16,Fhalf, he must have asked for.
OL,18,FThat is just what he got as the game
OL,19,Fwas pretty much taken away from
OL,20,FFreiburg, when Morgan Rogers scored to
OL,21,Fmake it three.
