PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779383153
OL,3,CAston Villa thrash Freiburg in
OL,4,CIstanbul to win first European trophy
OL,5,Cin 44 years
OL,7,FThe last time Aston Villa contested a
OL,8,FEuropean final was when they beat
OL,9,FBayern Munich in Rotterdam in 1982, to
OL,10,Fwin the then European Cup.
OL,12,FThe last time Aston Villa won a trophy
OL,13,Fwas the League Cup in 1996 after
OL,14,Fdefeating Leeds 3-0 at Wembley.
OL,16,FPrince William also joined fans in the
OL,17,Fstands to watch his team.
OL,19,FThe win means it's Head Coach Unai
OL,20,FEmery's seventh Europa League final.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
